                "category": "interaction",
                "description": {
                    "value": "<p>The spark of the soul used to create a masque mannequin is infused into its mask. A creature can break a masque mannequin's soul mask with a @Check[athletics|dc:40] check or steal it with a @Check[thievery|dc:40] check. If its mask is broken or removed, a masque mannequin must attempt a @Check[fortitude|dc:40] save.</p><hr /><p><strong>Critical Success</strong> The masque mannequin's animating spark shifts to infuse its body; it is unaffected and no longer has a soul mask.</p>\n<p><strong>Success</strong> The masque mannequin takes @Damage[2d6[persistent,mental]] damage. If it regains its mask, it can place it back on its face as an Interact action to automatically stop this persistent mental damage.</p>\n<p><strong>Failure</strong> As success, but @Damage[4d6[persistent,mental]] damage and @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.Stunned]{Stunned 1}.</p>\n<p><strong>Critical Failure</strong> As failure, but @Damage[8d6[persistent,mental]] damage and @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.Stunned]{Stunned 3}.</p>"
                },
